            <p class="comment-content">生老病死与鸡毛蒜皮，都用平静又带着淡淡温暖的语句娓娓道来。生活是最好的编剧。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="942662032">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-942662032" class="vote-count">5</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-942662032" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="942662032">有用</a>
